{
  "stem": "12868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't have to-- to have a pencil that [? you could use in Dachau. ?] Didn't have any paper to write in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You lost there?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I never been punished in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Especially punished, you know, that--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Children in that camp?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No children at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The children-- the children with the old people, they made be killed right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before they took the children, before they make the action for children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call in another children action.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took all the children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came in with big trucks in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the-- they threw the children like they were throwing rocks with- with-- with records, you know, music, hard music, you know, not-- not to the people or the mothers, not-- not to hear how the children cried.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody saw this, not me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I been in a coma.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been in-- that's what-- You see, I didn't remember my liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wish I would remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody-- everybody know about the liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Army, the American Army came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're kissing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they're hugging each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They dance in the streets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't see this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I been-- I open-- I opened my-- never even seen American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, one time in ghetto, in-- in-- in Dachau, came from the Red Cross, came, some of them, they give every one of them a can of [INAUDIBLE], a [INAUDIBLE] of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My old friend, [INAUDIBLE] his meat, he got it in barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When he see the canned [INAUDIBLE], he hold the canned [INAUDIBLE] and he drink out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he fall down like this, passed away from the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And later they say, who want to leave better not drink the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
